    <h3 class="font-semibold mt-6 mb-4 text-base">More on this story</h3>
    <ul class="text-xs">
                    <li class="leading-tight mb-4 flex items-center xl:items-start">
                <span class="flex items-center rounded-full bg-black-900 w-4 h-4 mr-2 xl:mt-1"><svg class="w-5 h-5" version="1.1" viewBox="0 0 36 36" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><path d="M15 9l-2.12 2.12 6.88 6.88 -6.88 6.88 2.12 2.12 9-9Z" fill="#fff"></path><path fill="none" d="M0 0h36v36h-36Z"></path></svg></span>
                <a href="https://news.stv.tv/scotland/scotland-records-722-suspected-drug-deaths-in-first-half-of-2021" class="hover:underline font-semibold">Scotland records 722 suspected drug deaths in first half of 2021</a>
            </li>
                    <li class="leading-tight mb-4 flex items-center xl:items-start">
                <span class="flex items-center rounded-full bg-black-900 w-4 h-4 mr-2 xl:mt-1"><svg class="w-5 h-5" version="1.1" viewBox="0 0 36 36" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><path d="M15 9l-2.12 2.12 6.88 6.88 -6.88 6.88 2.12 2.12 9-9Z" fill="#fff"></path><path fill="none" d="M0 0h36v36h-36Z"></path></svg></span>
                <a href="https://news.stv.tv/scotland/drug-deaths-hit-new-record-high-in-scotland-during-pandemic" class="hover:underline font-semibold">Drug deaths hit record high in Scotland during pandemic</a>
            </li>
